  "detailed_description": "HAELE 3D - Portrait Studio Lite is a 3D facial anatomy drawing reference tool designed for beginner to advanced artists. With a diverse range of editable characters, expressions, lighting setups and environments, it serves as a resource for learning how to draw human faces and heads. Whether your art style is realistic, stylized, cartoon, anime or anything in between this is easy to use app complements tutorials and aids practicing your portrait drawing or sculpting skills from sketch to finish.<br><br><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" ><span class=\"bb_img_ctn\"><video class=\"bb_img\" autoplay muted loop playsinline poster=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/2949950/extras/7689178a88d543f1bcafc8f624b7581d.poster.avif?t=1773168450\" width=600 height=338 ><source src=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/2949950/extras/7689178a88d543f1bcafc8f624b7581d.webm?t=1773168450\" type=\"video/webm; codecs=vp9\"><source src=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/2949950/extras/7689178a88d543f1bcafc8f624b7581d.mp4?t=1773168450\" type=\"video/mp4\"></video></span></p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" ><span class=\"bb_img_ctn\"><video class=\"bb_img\" autoplay muted loop playsinline poster=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/2949950/extras/cb594404dad56c1d2915b578e57252da.poster.avif?t=1773168450\" width=600 height=338 ><source src=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/2949950/extras/cb594404dad56c1d2915b578e57252da.webm?t=1773168450\" type=\"video/webm; codecs=vp9\"><source src=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/2949950/extras/cb594404dad56c1d2915b578e57252da.mp4?t=1773168450\" type=\"video/mp4\"></video></span></p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" ><span class=\"bb_img_ctn\"><video class=\"bb_img\" autoplay muted loop playsinline poster=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/2949950/extras/edcafb1c34dcdbcf79e5fe54dffaaf98.poster.avif?t=1773168450\" width=600 height=338 ><source src=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/2949950/extras/edcafb1c34dcdbcf79e5fe54dffaaf98.webm?t=1773168450\" type=\"video/webm; codecs=vp9\"><source src=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/2949950/extras/edcafb1c34dcdbcf79e5fe54dffaaf98.mp4?t=1773168450\" type=\"video/mp4\"></video></span></p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" >- Multiple characters: Choose from a variety of characters to practice drawing different facial structures.</p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" >- Expressions: Access a collection of ready-made expressions for quick inspiration.</p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" >- Editable Lights: Control the atmosphere with adjustable lighting, including 1 Point light (color, intensity, transformation), Environment light (HDRI map, intensity), and Ground light (color, intensity).</p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" >- Environment Options: Select from HDRI studio backgrounds, solid background colors, toggle floor visibility, and customize floor color and reflectivity.</p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" >- Adjustable Camera Settings: Fine-tune camera angles, locations, positions, and field of view for the perfect reference.</p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" >- Save and Load Scenes: Save your setups for future use and load them at any time.</p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" >- Load Presets: Quickly access predefined configurations to streamline your workflow.</p>",
  "about_the_game": "HAELE 3D - Portrait Studio Lite is a 3D facial anatomy drawing reference tool designed for beginner to advanced artists. With a diverse range of editable characters, expressions, lighting setups and environments, it serves as a resource for learning how to draw human faces and heads. Whether your art style is realistic, stylized, cartoon, anime or anything in between this is easy to use app complements tutorials and aids practicing your portrait drawing or sculpting skills from sketch to finish.<br><br><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" ><span class=\"bb_img_ctn\"><video class=\"bb_img\" autoplay muted loop playsinline poster=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/2949950/extras/7689178a88d543f1bcafc8f624b7581d.poster.avif?t=1773168450\" width=600 height=338 ><source src=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/2949950/extras/7689178a88d543f1bcafc8f624b7581d.webm?t=1773168450\" type=\"video/webm; codecs=vp9\"><source src=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/2949950/extras/7689178a88d543f1bcafc8f624b7581d.mp4?t=1773168450\" type=\"video/mp4\"></video></span></p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" ><span class=\"bb_img_ctn\"><video class=\"bb_img\" autoplay muted loop playsinline poster=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/2949950/extras/cb594404dad56c1d2915b578e57252da.poster.avif?t=1773168450\" width=600 height=338 ><source src=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/2949950/extras/cb594404dad56c1d2915b578e57252da.webm?t=1773168450\" type=\"video/webm; codecs=vp9\"><source src=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/2949950/extras/cb594404dad56c1d2915b578e57252da.mp4?t=1773168450\" type=\"video/mp4\"></video></span></p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" ><span class=\"bb_img_ctn\"><video class=\"bb_img\" autoplay muted loop playsinline poster=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/2949950/extras/edcafb1c34dcdbcf79e5fe54dffaaf98.poster.avif?t=1773168450\" width=600 height=338 ><source src=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/2949950/extras/edcafb1c34dcdbcf79e5fe54dffaaf98.webm?t=1773168450\" type=\"video/webm; codecs=vp9\"><source src=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/2949950/extras/edcafb1c34dcdbcf79e5fe54dffaaf98.mp4?t=1773168450\" type=\"video/mp4\"></video></span></p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" >- Multiple characters: Choose from a variety of characters to practice drawing different facial structures.</p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" >- Expressions: Access a collection of ready-made expressions for quick inspiration.</p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" >- Editable Lights: Control the atmosphere with adjustable lighting, including 1 Point light (color, intensity, transformation), Environment light (HDRI map, intensity), and Ground light (color, intensity).</p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" >- Environment Options: Select from HDRI studio backgrounds, solid background colors, toggle floor visibility, and customize floor color and reflectivity.</p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" >- Adjustable Camera Settings: Fine-tune camera angles, locations, positions, and field of view for the perfect reference.</p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" >- Save and Load Scenes: Save your setups for future use and load them at any time.</p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" >- Load Presets: Quickly access predefined configurations to streamline your workflow.</p>",
